                  Here, There and Everywhere Fares
           US Airways Sale Fares for 11 New York Cities
       Hurry! Purchase Tickets by Tuesday, February 26, 2002
       -----------------------------------------------------

US Airways is offering sale fares for travel between Albany, Buffalo, Rochester, Syracuse, Binghamton, Ithaca, Elmira, Jamestown, Massena, Ogdensburg, Watertown and US Airways cities throughout the US and the Caribbean.  Plus, book online
at http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/upstate_ny_sale.htm and save an additional 5% off these sale fares. 

Sale Details:
-------------
- Tickets must be purchased at least 14 days before departure and no 
  later than February 26, 2002
- Travel for all destinations must be completed by June 6, 2002
- Travel for Florida and the Caribbean is valid beginning April 8, 2002
- Travel Monday-Thursday for lowest sale fares
- See Sale Fare Requirements below for complete details


Dividend Miles Online Booking Bonus 
----------------------------------- 
Purchase a roundtrip ticket online and travel through June 6, 2002, and receive 1,000 bonus Dividend Miles.  Visit the Dividend Miles offers page at http://www.usairways.com/dividendmiles/offers/usairways.htm#booking for details on this and other Dividend Miles offers. 

 
This is just a sample of the sale fares offered.  Fares are good for travel in either direction.  For reservations and fares from your city go to http://www.usairways.com/promotions/specials/upstate_ny_sale.htm


